      • getStops

        public static ArrayList<Stop> getStops​(String date,
                                       int limit,
                                       int pageNumber)
        Gets a list of stop on the given date with a limit and page number. It is used to get stops on the day where the stops exceeded 100.
        Parameters:
        date - The date of the stops to get
        limit - The number of maximum stops to get. Maximum value is 100.
        pageNumber - The page number of the stops to get
        Returns:
        List<Stop> A list of stops based on the given arguments
